        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nMohamed, I don't think we should be writing junits for POJO's. In sonar coverage, we should be excluding junit coverage for generated source code and pojo objects as it provides no value. Junit is supposed to provide coverage of logic and execution of a unit of code. There is no logic in POJO's. Please abandon all your POJO's junits and exclude that package.",
